{"tid":1563280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以正視聽 唔該唔好再話唱願榮光歸香港等 海闊天空 變雨革膠化乜乜柒柒","createTime":"2019-09-12T10:45:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T20:18:20.000Z","uid":11254,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7c95821b04ba0b88b9dba4f76234e2dc3a8975c9","tid":1563280,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:45:34.000Z","msg":"首先隻歌內容擺明就係輸出革命 <br />\n並唔係一隻流行曲可以相提並論<br />\n第二就係身份認同 我地要日日唱 去洗人腦 <br />\n去增強香港人嘅民族意識 中共最驚就係咁<br />\n呢樣亦係中共經常做 你睇佢成日想立國歌法就知<br />\n同埋無人話唱歌就唔做其他野 <br />\n圍狗屋又話送頭 咁平日唱下歌有咩問題？<br />\n星期六日咪行動囉 有咩問題 <br />\n同雨革完全兩回事黎 <br />\n唔好再話左膠野 膠化 又輸 唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8920a9a47ced8397eb64ee6b382bb3b1cb70233e","tid":1563280,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:45:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"1acd984f707363eb259d269a1f7d7465ad7d65a0","tid":1563280,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:45:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ebe2427589d21b9efa12f836b6a60e49b360bf9e","tid":1563280,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:47:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a53f3f0c96a4ad3641c9b6b52de46a11ba9c05c","tid":15